d": 5, "text": "个人认为人类的发展的历史就是哲学史，黑格尔的辩证法就有这么个意思。", "timestamp": 1651756682}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 99116, "create_time": 1651757032, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "如果给现代进步文明（区别于中国古代那种落后文明）找一个源头的话，绝对离不开古希腊哲学。在此基础上发展出基督教文明，加上其他各种因素的融合，才有了近代人类的大发展。唯名论与实在论，理性与信仰，唯理主义与经验主义，持哪一种观点决定了一个人，一个民族，甚至整个人类的命运。", "timestamp": 1651757032}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 99139, "create_time": 1651757617, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "感谢诸位的回答，其实我就是推书bot（doge），作为半个哲学系学生，常常遇到有同学不理解甚至反对哲学，于是开了这个洞想探探你清学生对哲学的看法", "timestamp": 1651757617}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 99146, "create_time": 1651757698, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 感谢Eve的长篇回答，这是遇到同行了🤣🤣🤣", "timestamp": 1651757698}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 99203, "create_time": 1651758801, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 那我这属于是大放厥词了🤣", "timestamp": 1651758801}], "create_time": 1651754374, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1651758801, "likenum": 7, "n_attentions": 7, "n_comments": 12, "pid": 36175, "poll": null, "reply": 12, "text": "#36012\n哲学有什么用处呢，非引战，理性讨论🧐", "timestamp": 1651754374}}